{"tid":2139884,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得龍門好犀利","createTime":"2020-08-04T14:47:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T19:56:31.000Z","uid":61348,"like":12,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8712033c90d47953fc4a25ab46d94d18671c5ba4","tid":2139884,"uid":61348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T14:47:22.000Z","msg":"龍門從來唔會正面回應批評 有人指出問題請pr屌人分化<br />\n<br />\n港共對黃店都唔會咁無情 但龍門係第一人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大黃店蝦小黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由用黃圈厄飯食 剝削員工 聖誕卡事件 狗糧賣到60幾蚊碟搵傻仔笨 <br />\n樣樣野都可以幫鋪頭賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成為埋黃圈最大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家告埋其他黃店最後做到壟斷黃圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啊老闆果然利害 商業奇才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221200ef5487aeaa10d9a8f4e02edec8c1dd2344","tid":2139884,"uid":48083,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T14:48:51.000Z","msg":"Fb正面回應過好多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五毛勿回<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/juOuo5O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjuOuo5O.png&h=a867faf2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"136142144586984babe722de67d260ba79b6c7ef","tid":2139884,"uid":61348,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"221200ef5487aeaa10d9a8f4e02edec8c1dd2344","tid":2139884,"uid":48083,"like":15,"dislike